(1759, 'Surgery', 'PM2294. Ankle–brachial Pressure Index (ABPI)', '<div _ngcontent-smq-c132=\\ class=\ng-tns-c132-18 ng-star-inserted\ style=\\>\n      <div _ngcontent-smq-c132=\\ class=\ng-tns-c132-18 ng-star-inserted\><p>The <strong>ankle-brachial Pressure Index (ABPI)</strong> is the <strong>ratio of systolic pressure at the ankle to that in the arm.</strong></p>\n<p>The numerator is the highest pressure in the dorsalis pedis, posterior tibial, or peroneal artery and the denominator is the highest brachial systolic pressure.</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>ABPI Reading</td>\n<td>Interpretation</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&gt;0.9 to &lt;1.4</td>\n<td>Normal</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&lt;0.9</td>\n<td>Diagnostic of occlusive arterial disease&nbsp;in patients with symptoms of claudication or other signs of ischemia</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>0.5 to 0.9</td>\n<td>Arterial obstruction often associated with claudication</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&lt;0.4</td>\n<td>Critical limb ischemia (multilevel obstruction i.e any combination of iliac, femoral or tibial vessel disease and may be associated with non-healing ulcerations, ischemic rest pain, or pedal gangrene.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&gt;1.4</td>\n<td>Signifies poor compressibility of the arteries. Mostly due to calcification because of increased age, diabetes etc.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Note:&nbsp;A fall in the resting ABPI of more than 20% after exercise is indicative of arterial disease.<br><br></p></div><!---->\n      <!---->\n    </div><div _ngcontent-smq-c132=\\ class=\ng-tns-c132-18 ng-star-inserted\ style=\\>\n      <!---->\n      <div _ngcontent-smq-c132=\\ class=\ng-tns-c132-18 ng-star-inserted\>\n        <img _ngcontent-smq-c132=\\ class=\img-responsive ng-tns-c132-18 ng-star-inserted\ src=\https://dhmbxeygs57ff.cloudfront.net/uploads/a4a28e64a1194038b7da810b44d924cbx1280x1892.JPEG\><!---->\n      </div><!---->\n    </div><!---->'),
(1760, 'Surgery', 'PM2292. CEAP Classification of Chronic Lower Extremity Venous Disease', '<div _ngcontent-smq-c132=\\ class=\ng-tns-c132-18 ng-star-inserted\ style=\\>\n      <div _ngcontent-smq-c132=\\ class=\ng-tns-c132-18 ng-star-inserted\><div class=\page\ title=\Page 1027\>\n<table><colgroup><col><col><col> </colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\3\>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<div class=\page\ title=\Page 995\>\n<div class=\section\>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p>CEAP (Clinical-Etiology-Anatomy-Pathophysiology)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\3\ rowspan=\1\>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p><strong>Clinical&nbsp;classification (C)*</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\2\ rowspan=\1\>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p>C0</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p>No visible or palpable signs of venous disease</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\2\ rowspan=\1\>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p>C1</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p>Telangiectases or reticular veins</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\2\ rowspan=\1\>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p>C2</p>\n<p>C2r</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p>Varicose veins</p>\n<p>Recurrent varicose veins</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\2\ rowspan=\1\>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p>C3</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p>Edema</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\2\ rowspan=\1\>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p>C4</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\layoutArea\>\n<div class=\column\>\n<p>Ch